cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "GAIO Validation Lab"
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-03-09"
abstract: >
  A scientific test environment for measuring how different HTML markup
  techniques (JSON-LD, Semantic HTML, ARIA, noscript fallbacks, Declarative
  Shadow DOM, Microdata) affect content extraction by AI crawlers and large
  language models from Web Components with Shadow DOM encapsulation.
  Eight isolated variants enable controlled benchmarking of each GAIO
  (Generative AI Optimization) measure independently.
authors:
